sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CLI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ModelMesh Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant Service as modelmesh-serving<br/>ClusterIP Service
    participant RestProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Pod<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Model Deployment via InferenceService

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate ServingRuntime<br/>TLS: cert-manager CA
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>etcd: Store model metadata<br/>Optional auth

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Model Inference Request (REST)

    Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Application-defined
    Service->>RestProxy: Forward HTTP request
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Query model location<br/>HTTP
    etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model routing info
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Load model request<br/>gRPC

    alt Model not loaded
        Adapter->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM/Access Keys
        S3-->>Adapter: Model files
        Adapter->>ModelServer: Load model<br/>gRPC 8001
    end

    Adapter->>ModelServer: Inference request<br/>gRPC 8085
    ModelServer-->>Adapter: Prediction result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: gRPC response
    RestProxy-->>Service: HTTP response
    Service-->>Client: JSON prediction

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 3: Model Inference Request (gRPC)

    Client->>Service: gRPC InferRequest<br/>8033/TCP
    Service->>ModelMesh: Forward gRPC
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Query metadata
    etcd-->>ModelMesh: Routing info
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to model
    Adapter->>ModelServer: Execute inference<br/>8085/TCP
    ModelServer-->>Adapter: Result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>Service: gRPC response
    Service-->>Client: InferResponse
